            "title": "ACADEMIC PLANDEMIC.",
            "slug": "academic-plandemic-untitled",
            "html": "<hr><p><em>Financial Lessons from these times. Why it pays to build a Noahâ€™s ark. Today. Everyday. For the Next Pandemic!</em></p><p>Really, the biggest effect of this pandemic is the massive holes, that we have often ignored, that were revealed in a big way. As at this time of writing, there are 4.64million cases worldwide (5,959 in Nigeria) with three hundred and twelve thousand deaths - 182 in Nigeria. (Updated for May 18th) <br><br></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/675/1*A4TdNqGI0YvcPhTDSgUDvg.png\" class=\"kg-image\"><figcaption>COVID-19 Case Update (Nigeria)</figcaption></figure><p>And yet I maintain that it is not the biggest impact. The biggest impact was in realizing how unprepared Nigeria was for a pandemic. How the health sector wasnâ€™t well equipped initially, the great difficulty in providing social welfare by the government, and the level of extreme dependency of a large portion of Nigeria on their monthly income.</p><p>These are some of the issues that we have always known on some level but were made obvious by the situation. There are many more issues, for example, the fact that we had to create a campaign reminding people to have the level of basic hygiene that we should have already known from home economics classes was rather disturbing.</p><blockquote>the health sector wasnâ€™t well equipped initially, the great difficulty in providing social welfare by the government, and the level of extreme dependency of a large portion of Nigeria on their monthly income</blockquote><h3 id=\"the-noah-s-rule\"><strong>THE NOAHâ€™S RULE</strong></h3><p>But challenges are pointers to areas that need improvement and here at <a href=\"http://InvestNaira.com/Signup\" rel=\"noopener\">InvestNaira </a>we have come up with some of the lessons that everyone needs to learn in handling their finances. Over the next couple of weeks weâ€™d be looking at the tips at length, helping to increase your financial intelligence.</p><p>Today weâ€™ll be looking at the first, and in my opinion, the most important lesson; <strong><em>The need for an emergency fund</em></strong>. To illustrate this, I will be drawing parallels between this current situation and a very common bible story that a lot of us should have heard of. The story of Noah.</p><blockquote><strong>The Noah Rule</strong> says: â€œPredicting rain doesnâ€™t count, building an <strong>ark</strong> does.â€ <br>(Warren Buffetâ€Šâ€”â€Š2001 Shareholder Letter)</blockquote><p>For those who donâ€™t know the story Iâ€™ll briefly summarize. God was going to send a flood to destroy the world due to the high level of evil that the people were exhibiting. But He decided to spare Noah because he did right in his sight. So he was instructed to build an ark for himself, his family and two (male and female) out of every living thing. The floods came and the ones who survived were those who were within the ark.</p><p><strong>How Does Building A Noahâ€™s Ark Affect Finance?</strong></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card kg-card-hascaption\"><blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B_SWlwfjgm1/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" data-instgrm-version=\"12\" style=\" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);\"><div style=\"padding:16px;\"> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B_SWlwfjgm1/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" style=\" background:#FFFFFF; line-height:0; padding:0 0; text-align:center; text-decoration:none; width:100%;\" target=\"_blank\"> <div style=\" display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;\"> <div style=\"background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;\"></div> <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;\"> <div style=\" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;\"></div> <div style=\" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;\"></div></div></div><div style=\"padding: 19% 0;\"></div> <div style=\"display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;\"><svg width=\"50px\" height=\"50px\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"https://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><g transform=\"translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)\" fill=\"#000000\"><g><path d=\"M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 C561.058,72.155 560.06,72.803 558.662,73.347 C557.607,73.757 556.021,74.244 553.102,74.378 C549.944,74.521 548.997,74.552 541,74.552 C533.003,74.552 532.056,74.521 528.898,74.378 C525.979,74.244 524.393,73.757 523.338,73.347 C521.94,72.803 520.942,72.155 519.894,71.106 C518.846,70.057 518.197,69.06 517.654,67.663 C517.244,66.606 516.755,65.022 516.623,62.101 C516.479,58.943 516.448,57.996 516.448,50 C516.448,42.003 516.479,41.056 516.623,37.899 C516.755,34.978 517.244,33.391 517.654,32.338 C518.197,30.938 518.846,29.942 519.89