nslateX(0px) translateY(7px);\"></div> <div style=\"background-color: #F4F4F4; height: 12.5px; transform: rotate(-45deg) translateX(3px) translateY(1px); width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;\"></div> <div style=\"background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);\"></div></div><div style=\"margin-left: 8px;\"> <div style=\" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;\"></div> <div style=\" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg)\"></div></div><div style=\"margin-left: auto;\"> <div style=\" width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);\"></div> <div style=\" background-color: #F4F4F4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);\"></div> <div style=\" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);\"></div></div></div></a> <p style=\" margin:8px 0 0 0; padding:0 4px;\"> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B_SWlwfjgm1/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" style=\" color:#000; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none; word-wrap:break-word;\" target=\"_blank\">Building wealth for the long term is really essential, especially in times like this.  Sure you may be tempted to spend a little more since we all are at home, but controlling how you doing money and even saving more will only do you more good in the long run This is what we live by @investnaira and you also can be party of this journey to long term wealth today. Click on out bio to learn more #savings #investment #investnaira #longterm #naijabusiness</a></p> <p style=\" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;\">A post shared by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/investnaira/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" style=\" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px;\" target=\"_blank\"> InvestNaira</a> (@investnaira) on <time style=\" font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px;\" datetime=\"2020-04-22T14:37:48+00:00\">Apr 22, 2020 at 7:37am PDT</time></p></div></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"//www.instagram.com/embed.js\"></script><figcaption>Build.</figcaption></figure><p>The job of Noahâ€™s ark was security. No matter the rains, no matter the floods, no matter how long, the ark kept them. And the ark didnâ€™t appear from nowhere, it was built. It was built in response to the fact that a flood was coming. With finances today, too many people are living without an ark.</p><p>Nothing to protect them from when the floods come. And oh, yes, they would come! You could say pandemics are rare, but emergencies generally are a lot more common. We all hope to avoid these, but fires, accidents, sicknesses, job loss, all happen to people daily. And these current corona times show this more than ever. When a lockdown was looking inevitable, I heard someone comment that those without an emergency fund would struggle in these times. And itâ€™s heartbreaking how right they were. So many people who depend on their daily, weekly or monthly income to survive became anxious. How were they supposed to survive? How were we all to survive?</p><blockquote>And the ark didnâ€™t appear from nowhere, it was built.</blockquote><h3 id=\"build-an-ark-today\">Build an Ark! Today</h3><p>The inevitability of things like these is the major reason why InvestNaira existâ€Šâ€”â€Što help you build a Financial Ark that would always cater to you, pandemics or emergencies. One that is durable and would help you when difficult times arise. Through our SICâ€Šâ€”â€ŠSaving Smartly, Investing Wisely and Compounding again and againâ€Šâ€”â€Šformula and educating you on financial intelligent ark building, we would help you building a solid financial ark for surviving and navigating financial floods, as and when they come!</p><p>We will survive this and when we do, we would be here to help you recover your lost ground and start/continue building an ark for your future.</p><p>Whatâ€™s left to start? You can begin today, an Ark to Build!</p><hr><p><em>Oludipe Bolusere Ayobambo </em><a href=\"http://facebook.com/investnaira\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><em>| </em></strong><em>Save | Invest | Build An Ark</em></a>!</p><p>Follow us on Socials @<a href=\"https://medium.com/u/2da0e019decd?source=post_page-----46eaf3675659----------------------\" rel=\"noopener\">InvestNaira</a></p>",
